<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <style>
        .container-user {
            width: 95%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .profile-actions-container {
            flex-basis: 30%;
            padding: 0 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .profile-info-container {
            flex-basis: 70%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .profile-info {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .profile-picture {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 5px solid #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .profile-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .profile-username {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .profile-details {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .profile-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .profile-details label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }

        .profile-bio {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #444;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .profile-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .profile-action {
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background-color: #bfc2c5;
            color: #181717;
            border: 2px solid #32363a;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .profile-action:hover {
            background-color: #f5f7f8;
        }

        .profile-action i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
    </style>
    <%- include ('partials/head/head.ejs' ) %>

    <body>
        <%- include('partials/header/header.ejs') %>
        <!-- breadcrumb-section -->
        <div class="breadcrumb-section breadcrumb-bg">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2 text-center">
                        <div class="breadcrumb-text">
                            <p>Fresh and Organic</p>
                            <h1>User Profile</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- end breadcrumb section -->
        <div class="container-user">
            <div class="profile-actions-container">
                <div class="profile-actions">
                    <a href="#" class="profile-action update-profile">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-edit"></i>
                        Update Profile</a>
                    <a href="#" class="profile-action continue-shopping">
                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                        Continue Shopping</a>
                    <a href="#" class="profile-action change-password">
                        <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                        Change Password</a>
                    <a href="#" class="profile-action wallet">
                        <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
                        Wallet</a>
                    <a href="order-history-page.html" class="profile-action order-history">
                        <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                        Order History</a>
                    <a href="#" class="profile-action logout">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
                        Logout</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-info-container">
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <div class="profile-header">
                        <img class="profile-picture" src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Profile Picture">
                        <div class="profile-name">John Doe</div>
                        <div class="profile-username">@johndoe</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-details">
                        <p>
                            <label>Email:</label>
                            johndoe@example.com</p>
                        <p>
                            <label>Location:</label>
                            New York, USA</p>
                        <p>
                            <label>Joined:</label>
                            January 1, 2020</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-bio">
                        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nulla varius libero quis erat dictum, sit amet laoreet dui varius. Proin sit amet tristique velit. Duis id sem nisi.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('./partials/footer/footer.ejs') %>
    </body>
</html>
